{"word":"H8489 - תֵּימָנִי - Têymânîy - tay-maw-nee' - Temani","slug":"H8489","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">תֵּימָנִי</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>Têymânîy"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>tay-maw-nee'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Temani"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"Original: <b><he>תּימני</he></b> <p />Transliteration: <b>têymânı̂y</b> <p />Phonetic: <b>tay-maw-nee'</b> <p class=\"bdb_def\"><b>BDB Definition</b>:</p> Temanite or Temani = see Teman \" southward\" <ol><li>an inhabitant of Teman located east of Idumea</li><li>a descendant of Teman, the grandson of Esau and a duke of Edom</li></ol> <p />Origin: patronymically from <a href=\"#/H8487\">H8487</a> <p />TWOT entry: None <p />Part(s) of speech: Proper Name Masculine "},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H3225\">H3225</a>, <a href=\"#/H3226\">H3226</a>, <a href=\"#/H3227\">H3227</a>, <a href=\"#/H3228\">H3228</a>, <a href=\"#/H3231\">H3231</a>, <a href=\"#/H3232\">H3232</a>, <a href=\"#/H3233\">H3233</a>, <a href=\"#/H541\">H541</a>, <a href=\"#/H8486\">H8486</a>, <a href=\"#/H8487\">H8487</a>, <a href=\"#/H8488\">H8488</a>"}]}